5 Light'; font-size:11pt"> et al.</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">, 2012)</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">. T</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">here is some evidence </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">to suggest </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">that this </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">aspect of the encounter with a professional homeopath </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">may explain homeopath</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">y’s therapeutic </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">effectiveness (Jacobs</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> et al.</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">,</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> 2005; </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Brien et al.,</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">2010</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">)</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">.</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> Indeed, t</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">his</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> can be considered as </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">the </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">most </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45