><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">also </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">found that 90% of </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">complementary and alternative medicine (</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">CAM</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">)</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> provision is purchased privately</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> with total expenditure est</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">imated at £450 million for</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">1998</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">, </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">with</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> 10% of the adult population contact</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">ing</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> a CAM practitioner that year</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">. </span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">In addition to the </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">clear</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">demand</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> for CAM healthcare in supporting patients with </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; fo